{
  "slug": "括号匹配问题",
  "title": "括号匹配问题",
  "type": "知识点",
  "tags": [],
  "difficulty": null,
  "summary": "",
  "link": "",
  "link_text": "",
  "source": "",
  "aliases": [],
  "parent": "经典问题",
  "format": "markdown",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "构造 +1/-1 前缀和",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "合法序列的充要条件：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "1. 任意位置的前缀和 $\\ge 0$；",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "2. 最终总和 $= 0$。",
          "depth": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "一对匹配的括号<code>()</code>进行合法翻转（<code>()</code>变成<code>)(</code>）需要满足的条件：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "设 $s[i] = (, s[j] = ), i < j$，需满足 $min(pre[i],...,pre[j - 1]) \\ge 2$。",
          "depth": 3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "最长合法括号子序列",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "括号子序列（不要求连续）的最长合法长度结论：",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "$$M = \\min_{0 \\le p \\le n} \\big( \\text{前缀}[1..p] \\text{中 \\texttt{(} 的个数} + \\text{后缀}[p+1..n] \\text{中 \\texttt{)} 的个数} \\big)$$",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "答案为 $2M$。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "heading": "证明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>第一步：</strong>$\\le \\min$<strong>（上界）</strong>",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "固定一个分割点 $p$，把序列切成前缀 $[1..p]$ 和后缀 $[p+1..n]$。",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "任取一对匹配的括号 <code>(</code>...<code>)</code>，<code>(</code> 必须在 <code>)</code> 前面。所以这对括号的位置<strong>只有三种可能</strong>：",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "两个都在前缀 → 消耗前缀里一个 <code>(</code>",
              "depth": 4
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "两个都在后缀 → 消耗后缀里一个 <code>)</code>",
              "depth": 4
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<code>(</code> 在前缀、<code>)</code> 在后缀 → 同时消耗前缀 <code>(</code> 和后缀 <code>)</code>",
              "depth": 4
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "第四种\"<code>)</code> 在前缀且 <code>(</code> 在后缀\"<strong>不可能出现</strong>，因为那样右括号在左括号前面。",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "所以每对匹配括号<strong>至少</strong>对前缀的 <code>(</code> 池或后缀的 <code>)</code> 池贡献一次消耗。因此：",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$\\text{匹配对数} \\le \\text{前缀中 \\texttt{(} 的个数} + \\text{后缀中 \\texttt{)} 的个数}$$",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "这个不等式对<strong>任意</strong> $p$ 都成立。取所有 $p$ 中最紧的那个上界，即得 $\\le \\min$。",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>第二步：能取到等号</strong>",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "设 $\\min$ 在 $p^*$ 处取到，值为 $M$。贪心构造：从左往右取 $M$ 个 <code>(</code>，从右往左取 $M$ 个 <code>)</code>，按顺序配对即可得到 $2M$ 长的合法子序列。因此等号可达。",
              "depth": 3
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "例子",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>例 1</strong>：<code>())(()</code>",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$p=1$：前缀 <code>(1)</code> 有 1 个 <code>(</code>，后缀 <code>))(()</code> 有 2 个 <code>)</code> → 上界 $1+2=3$ 对",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$p=3$：前缀 <code>())</code> 有 1 个 <code>(</code>，后缀 <code>(()</code> 有 2 个 <code>)</code> → 上界 $1+2=3$ 对",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\min = 3$，最长合法子序列 $2 \\times 3 = 6$（去掉中间俩 <code>)</code>，得 <code>()()()</code>）",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>例 2</strong>：<code>)))(()(((</code>",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$p=2$：前缀 <code>))</code> 有 0 个 <code>(</code>，后缀 <code>)(()(((</code> 有 2 个 <code>)</code> → 上界 $0+2=2$ 对",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$p=3$：前缀 <code>)))</code> 有 0 个 <code>(</code>，后缀 <code>(()(((</code> 有 1 个 <code>)</code> → 上界 $0+1=1$ 对（<strong>瓶颈</strong>）",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$\\min = 1$，最长合法子序列仅 $2$ 个字符（从中间挑一对 <code>()</code>）",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "直观感受：左边全是 <code>)</code> 右边全是 <code>(</code>，两端资源对不上，min 自然小。",
              "depth": 3
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
